                        <interp inst="t18381231-name-233" type="given" value="EDWARD"></interp>EDWARD SCOTNEY</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable T</hi> 79.) I was called, and took the</p>
               <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="183812310026"></xptr>
               <p>prisoner. I found him in the barge, and this rope was in the cabin—the prisoner said Mr. Marsden's people told him to <hi rend="italic">go</hi> on board their barge and take the rope to his, to take care of it—the barge he was on board of was 100 yards from the prosecutor's—they were both on the Grand Junc<lb></lb>tion Canal.</p>
